                            <comment id="12936690" author="aco" created="Thu, 11 Jan 2007 09:57:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix added to r495172&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Added a activemq.classpath system property to extend the classpath of activemq&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By default it contains activemq.home/conf.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It can be extended by specifying additional paths via the ACTIVEMQ_CLASSPATH environment variable separated by semi-colons.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
